flowchart TB
  User[Authenticated user] --> HTTPS[Global HTTPS Load Balancer]
  Internet[Untrusted internet] --> HTTPS
  HTTPS --> Armor[Cloud Armor WAF]
  Armor --> IAP[Identity-Aware Proxy]
  IAP --> NEG[Serverless NEG]
  NEG --> Run[Cloud Run service]
  Run --> RuntimeSA[Runtime service account]
  Armor --> Logs[Cloud Logging]
  IAP --> Logs
  Run --> Logs

